# {{context|physics|lang=en}} A [[point]], near or [[within]] a [[body]], through which its [[weight]] can be [[assumed]] to act when considering forces on the body and its motion under gravity. This coincides with the [[center of mass]] in a [[uniform]] [[gravitational]] [[field]].
